ISLAMABAD, Oct 24 (APP):Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib on Sunday expressed grief and sorrow over the sad demise of wife of journalist Sanaullah Khan.
In a condolence message, he prayed for the highest rank in Jannah for the deceased and sympathized with bereaved family.
